<hymn_number>11046</hymn_number>
<title>bḥbk yʿzf qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥbk rby yʿzf qlby .. ạ̉lḥạn frḥiⁿ wslạm
 thtf nfsy kly lrby .. qlby wḥby wạlạ̉yạm
 ạlqrạr- mḥbty ạ̹lyk rby .. ạ̉yạ rfyqy fy kl drby
 tẖbt qlby bk wzd ḥby lk .. ạ̉nt ạ̉yạ ḥbyb wlys gẖyrk
 2- bḥbk rby ldẖ ḥdytẖy .. yạ ʿzạʾ nfsy fy ạlậlạm
 tusẖfy̱ ʿẓạmy tḥyạ bfrḥiⁿ .. yfyḍ qlby bạlslạm
 3- bḥbk rby ạ̉ṭrḥ kẖwfy .. fy ṣlyb fạdyã ạlḥnwn
 ḥytẖ dmạk blsm rwḥy .. tusẖfy̱ jrạḥy wạlsẖjwn
 4- bḥbk rby yḥlw lnfsy .. kwny sfyraⁿạ llḥbyb
 yʿlw ndạỷy hyạ lrby .. hyạ ạ̹lyh fhw qryb</lyrics>
</song>